Class BigDecimalField

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.scene.control.Skinnable

    public class BigDecimalField
extends javafx.scene.control.Control

    Input field for BigDecimal values. This control has the following features: <ul> <li>BigDecimal number is parsed and formatted according to the provided NumberFormat</li> <li>getter/setter for BigDecimal and (formatted) String representation of the number value</li> <li>up/down arrow keys and buttons increment/decrement the number by stepwidth</li> <li>If minValueProperty() and/or maxValue are set, values outside these boundaries are not accepted for number</li> </ul>
